- candidate test
    - configuration\ == different set ups
        - chromedriver
        - default.yml == credentials, API
        - geckodrvier
    - features\
        - step_definitions == actual code
            - rest_tests_steps.rb # code for API
            - web_ui_steps.rb # code for browser
        - support\
            - helpers\
                - class_extentions.rb == class modifications
                - logger.rb == logging definition
                - rest_wrapper.rb == API modifications
                - scenario_data.rb == data
                - step_helper.rb == helper
            - env.rb == aka conftest.py
            - hoooks.rb == aka fixtures
        - rest_api_test.feature == business explanations of the feature
        - web_page_test.feature == business explanations of the feature
    - .ruby-gemset == isolated environment 
    - .ruby-version == version
    - Gemfile == libraries and packages
    